{"tid":1349763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如向黑社會做文宣，導人向善","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T11:13:44.000Z","uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f327608e7298d8f6eed7be81798f8dacde2dd8ec","tid":1349763,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:07:34.000Z","msg":"即係令佢哋改邪歸正<br />\n減少社會動盪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對佢哋做文宣<br />\n一定要用激將法<br />\n分裂佢地<br />\n好似話<br />\n「A辦事人妻兒受襲擊，故欺善怕惡，有仇不報」<br />\n有埋圖<br />\n做埋無賴文宣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之唱到佢哋勁冇面<br />\n令佢哋知道<br />\n間接令佢哋聲譽受損係邊個<br />\n之類嘅言論<br />\n佢地就最要面<br />\n家下班鄉下佬打市民<br />\n打傷人固然是大佬唔識教細<br />\n但係主要煽動策劃是何X堯<br />\n完全唔設底線<br />\n搞到啲黑社會認為冇王法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到啲細嘅打埋啲第啲圍頭佬老婆仔女<br />\n<br />\n就好似打仗咁<br />\n你會將茅頭指向最大嗰個<br />\n<br />\n依家就整文宣<br />\n再放喺唔同嘅討論區/fb gp上<br />\n你知班孫冇腦<br />\n乜都share<br />\n第時一傳十十傳百<br />\n搞到個辦事人好冇面<br />\n煩佢個幾兩個月<br />\n佢就真係做嘢<br />\n<br />\n何君X呢啲操控者<br />\n無理由比佢過得咁開心<br />\n一定班老黑要做啲嘢教訓佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係如果得閒就做<br />\n唔係分化戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4da071ad465e0147380452c627e36401af656e4","tid":1349763,"uid":189416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f327608e7298d8f6eed7be81798f8dacde2dd8ec","tid":1349763,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:07:34.000Z","msg":"即係令佢哋改邪歸正<br />\n減少社會動盪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif